Structs/FontDescription.html.name: FontDescription
Structs/FontDescription.html.abstract: FontDescription which can describe font, useful to create fonts represented by external model.

Protocols/DynamicTypeFont.html#/s:5Doric.name: preferredFont(forTextStyle:maximumPointSize:compatibleWith:)
Protocols/DynamicTypeFont.html#/s:5Doric.abstract: Dynamically scalled font for FontStyle with maximumPointSize & traitCollection.

Protocols/Font.html#/s:5Doric4FontP5font.name: fonts
Protocols/Font.html#/s:5Doric4FontP5font.abstract: List of fonts and their text style

Protocols/DynamicTypography.html#/s:5Dor.name: preferredFont(forTextStyle:)
Protocols/DynamicTypography.html#/s:5Dor.abstract: Returns an instance of the font for the specified FontStyle and scaled appropriately for the user’s selected content size category.

Protocols/Typography.html#/s:5Doric10Typ.name: font(forTextStyle:)
Protocols/Typography.html#/s:5Doric10Typ.abstract: Returns an instance of the font for the specified FontStyle and with font size.

Protocols/TypographyOptions.html#/s:5Dor.name: shouldScaleFont
Protocols/TypographyOptions.html#/s:5Dor.abstract: Adjust fonts as per content size category.

Protocols/DualThemeSwitcher.html#/s:5Dor.name: toggleTheme()
Protocols/DualThemeSwitcher.html#/s:5Dor.abstract: toggle current theme, replace current theme with alternate theme.

Protocols/LayoutValueRepresentable.html#.name: pixel
Protocols/LayoutValueRepresentable.html#.abstract: One pixel value based on device scale

Protocols/GradientColor.html#/s:5Doric13.name: endColor
Protocols/GradientColor.html#/s:5Doric13.abstract: End color of gradient, by default 0.5 ligher or darker of startColor

Protocols/GradientColor.html#/s:5Doric13.name: colors
Protocols/GradientColor.html#/s:5Doric13.abstract: Provides list of CGColor to create gradient using CAGradientLayer

Protocols/LightenColorSet.html.name: LightenColorSet
Protocols/LightenColorSet.html.abstract: LightenColorSet, represents lighter colors of base color.

Protocols/DarkenColorSet.html.name: DarkenColorSet
Protocols/DarkenColorSet.html.abstract: DarkenColorSet, represents darker colors of base color.

Protocols/ExtendedLightenColorSet.html.name: ExtendedLightenColorSet
Protocols/ExtendedLightenColorSet.html.abstract: LightenColorSet, represents lighter colors of base color.

Protocols/ExtendedDarkenColorSet.html.name: ExtendedDarkenColorSet
Protocols/ExtendedDarkenColorSet.html.abstract: ExtendedDarkenColorSet, represents extedend darker colors of base color.

Protocols/Color.html.name: Color
Protocols/Color.html.abstract: Color which represents base color, other palettes creates lighter and darker colors of base color.

Protocols/ColorPalette.html.name: ColorPalette
Protocols/ColorPalette.html.abstract: ColorPalette represents base color with set of lighter and darker colors of base, total 5 colors (shades and tints) are represented by ColorPalette.

Protocols/LargerColorPalette.html.name: LargerColorPalette
Protocols/LargerColorPalette.html.abstract: LargerColorPalette represents base color with set of lighter and darker colors of base, total 9 colors (shades and tints) are represented by ColorPalette.

Protocols/SemanticColorPalette.html.name: SemanticColorPalette
Protocols/SemanticColorPalette.html.abstract: Semantic color palette, used for messaging. Used to deliver information about success, error, warning.

Protocols/MainColorPalette.html.name: MainColorPalette
Protocols/MainColorPalette.html.abstract: A color palette which contains primary, secondary and supplimentory colors with their darker and lighter color sets.

Protocols/GradientColor.html.name: GradientColor
Protocols/GradientColor.html.abstract: GradientColor protocol provides gradient defination with start & end colors and start & end points. Helper to create gradient using CAGradientLayer.

Protocols/LayoutValueRepresentable.html.name: LayoutValueRepresentable
Protocols/LayoutValueRepresentable.html.abstract: Type which can reprent value, Mostly used with autolayouts, but not limited to it. Contains some utility methods to create margins, insets etc.

Protocols/Scale.html.name: Scale
Protocols/Scale.html.abstract: Scale represents small set of scale sizes.

Protocols/FullScale.html.name: FullScale
Protocols/FullScale.html.abstract: FullScale represents small set of scale sizes.

Protocols/ValueLevel.html.name: ValueLevel
Protocols/ValueLevel.html.abstract: ValueLevel represents set of level for a value.

Protocols/TwoStateValueLevel.html.name: TwoStateValueLevel
Protocols/TwoStateValueLevel.html.abstract: TwoStateValueLevel represents two state for a value.

Protocols/Style.html.name: Style
Protocols/Style.html.abstract: Style protocol represents style which can be applied on control

Protocols/Theme.html.name: Theme
Protocols/Theme.html.abstract: Represents them with color palette. Currenly supports only color palettes.

Protocols/DualThemeSwitcher.html.name: DualThemeSwitcher
Protocols/DualThemeSwitcher.html.abstract: DualThemeSwitcher holds two instance for theme, helper to create dual themes i.e light/dark mode or day/night mode.

Protocols/Typography.html.name: Typography
Protocols/Typography.html.abstract: Typography provides static size fonts as per FontStyle

Protocols/DynamicTypography.html.name: DynamicTypography
Protocols/DynamicTypography.html.abstract: DynamicTypography provides dynamic types fonts along with static size fonts

Protocols/FontConvertible.html.name: FontConvertible
Protocols/FontConvertible.html.abstract: A type with a customized font representation

Protocols/SystemFont.html.name: SystemFont
Protocols/SystemFont.html.abstract: SystemFont font which represents built in Font Style - UIFont.TextStyle.

Protocols/DynamicTypeFont.html.name: DynamicTypeFont
Protocols/DynamicTypeFont.html.abstract: Dynamically scalable font which supports built in textstyle - UIFont.TextStyle.

Protocols/DynamicTypeCustomTextStyleFont.name: DynamicTypeCustomTextStyleFont
Protocols/DynamicTypeCustomTextStyleFont.abstract: DynamicTypeCustomTextStyleFont - Support font with custom font style.

Extensions/UIFont.html#/s:So6UIFontC5Dor.name: default
Extensions/UIFont.html#/s:So6UIFontC5Dor.abstract: Fallback fonts wherever font operations failed to provide requested fonts.

Extensions/UIColor.html#/s:So7UIColorC5D.name: startColor
Extensions/UIColor.html#/s:So7UIColorC5D.abstract: Implements GradientColor protocol, by default current color is startColor for gradient defination

Extensions/UIColor.html#/s:So7UIColorC5D.name: hexString
Extensions/UIColor.html#/s:So7UIColorC5D.abstract: hexadecimal (a hex triplet) representation of current color.

Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.name: anchorEdges(_:constant:activated:priority:)
Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.abstract: Creates contraint to leading, trailing, top, bottom edges anchor.

Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.name: recursiveEnableBorder(_:color:width:)
Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.abstract: Add recursive border to view and all its subviews

Extensions/UIView/Guideline.html.name: Guideline
Extensions/UIView/Guideline.html.abstract: Shows guide for an instance of view, Guideline adds single line view with constraints equivalents to edges, dimentions, baselines.

Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.name: showGuide(guideline:color:)
Extensions/UIView.html#/s:So6UIViewC5Dor.abstract: Show guide for view with guideline options

Enums/LayoutRelation.html.name: LayoutRelation
Enums/LayoutRelation.html.abstract: LayoutRelation represents autolayout constraint relationship with other attribute.

Enums/Space.html.name: Space
Enums/Space.html.abstract: Space - represents default set of space sizes.

Classes/GradientView.html#/s:5Doric12Gra.name: init(gradient:)
Classes/GradientView.html#/s:5Doric12Gra.abstract: Convenience initializer to create an instance of GradientView using GradientColor

Classes/Doric.html#/s:5DoricAAC6sharedAB.name: shared
Classes/Doric.html#/s:5DoricAAC6sharedAB.abstract: Shared instance to access various properties and settings for graph debug view.

Classes/Doric.html#/s:5DoricAAC8isHidden.name: isHidden
Classes/Doric.html#/s:5DoricAAC8isHidden.abstract: A Boolean value that determines whether the debugger graph view is hidden.

Classes/Doric.html.name: Doric
Classes/Doric.html.abstract: Instance to access debug tools i.e. GraphView.

Typealiases.html.abstract: The following type aliases are available globally.
